(47, 1, '2012-02-12 21:45:04', '2012-02-12 21:45:04', '<p>Nyligen fick jag i uppdrag att skapa ett spel fritt efter mina egna passioner. Jag som är ett stort fan av transformers sen jag var liten, jag kunde inte låta bli att låta robotarna inspirera mig. Uppgiften var att bygga en nivå men jag spann loss och utvecklade vidare på idéen för jag tyckte den var så rolig. Lade på extra egenskaper som ljud och svårighetsgrader.\n\nTanken är att i framtiden kunna bygga ut den genom att jag från början programerat den enligt ett AS3-framework jag byggt själv där jag använder mig av en version av ett "MVC-designpattern", så det blir enkelt att bygga på med andra olika nivåer eller/och spelmoduler. Spelet är alltså helt objektorienterat </p>', 'Transformers', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '29-autosave', '', '', '2012-02-12 21:45:04', '2012-02-12 21:45:04', '', 29, 'http://localhost/mikaeleng/29-autosave', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(468, 1, '2014-12-06 19:40:11', '2014-12-06 19:40:11', 'Sj had an intranet that was from 2003 in a CMS which did not support today\'s requirements for what an intranet will be used. SharePoint 2013 online was procured, and along this created a project that would row ashore the new intranet. It worked Mikael along with capabilities in the customer\'s organization to convey the idea and concept, developed materials and reconcile iterations of the control groups, reference groups, management groups. Michael was instrumental in keeping these groups to date on the intranet throughout the project. Michael was with and took out requirements specifications, check the log and sprint logs. Meanwhile, Michael worked closely with the development team and provided a complex prototype, so the link between sprint log and how it would interaction terms would work became evident. Because of the size of the company, Michael had a close communication with various representatives of the personas developed in a preliminary study. With them carried out Mikael user testing, interviews and sued the overall ideas and concepts.', 'SJ - intranet', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '464-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-06 19:40:11', '2014-12-06 19:40:11', '', 464, 'http://192.168.1.4/mikaeleng/464-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
