(469, 1, '2014-12-06 19:40:54', '2014-12-06 19:40:54', 'Wasa Kredit needed a new sales support which was a common system for the different sales divisions which at the time had several different kinds of applications. Mikael worked with Windows-specific interaction patterns and supported the rest of the development team with usability and information about user needs looked. Michael had frequent communication with users of various existing systems to while working meeting of usability. Michael made continuous usability testing with users by producing a complex prototype in Axure and used the same tools to communicate interaction with the rest of the development team. Michael also took up the A / B testing to ensure the system they used the best interaction patterns for the specific users\' mental model of the system.', 'Wasakredit', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '462-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-06 19:40:54', '2014-12-06 19:40:54', '', 462, 'http://192.168.1.4/mikaeleng/462-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
