(460, 1, '2013-12-05 12:00:39', '2013-12-05 12:00:39', 'One of my first assignments at HiQ was a new app for Mr Green in Germany. It is a app that is free to play, casino and other quick games in the app. The Challange was to make one single design framework for several different games with their own design interface. The app was developed in Russia and the UX/UI was developed in Sweden.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe app was built both for IOS and Android. we hade to take in consideration all the different sceen sizes, design guidelines and design patterns known by the users.', 'Skill games', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'mr-green', '', '', '2015-01-25 15:05:03', '2015-01-25 15:05:03', '', 0, 'http://192.168.1.4/mikaeleng/?p=460', 0, 'post', '', 0),
