(500, 1, '2014-12-15 13:53:16', '2014-12-15 13:53:16', 'One of my first assignments at HiQ was a new app for Mr Green in Germany. It is a app that is free to play, casino and other quick games in the app. The Challange was to make one single design framework for several different games with their own design interface. The app was developed in Russia and the UX/UI was developed in Sweden.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nThe app was built both for IOS and Android. we hade to take in consideration all the different sceen sizes, design guidelines and design patterns known by the users.', 'Mr Green', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '460-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-15 13:53:16', '2014-12-15 13:53:16', '', 460, 'http://www.mikaeleng.se/460-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(501, 1, '2015-04-01 21:59:28', '2015-04-01 21:59:28', 'Cambio wanted to create a new public website that was more communicative and modern. The site would be responsive and adapt to diffenrent screen sizes. Using a variety of internal workshops with the client and all the stakeholders at Cambio to generate an efficiency map with the different target groups and their needs. With the target groups mapped out I did interviews with the four main target groups. I performed usability tests and A / B tests for various interactive work flows to create the best user experience. We used SCRUM as project methodology where I also accounted for all requirements specification and testing.', 'A responsive web site', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '456-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-04-01 21:59:28', '2015-04-01 21:59:28', '', 456, 'http://www.mikaeleng.se/456-autosave-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
