(586, 1, '2015-01-25 15:10:26', '2015-01-25 15:10:26', 'One of my major projects at Nordnet bank was developing their new blog site. The site was built in wordpress and had stakeholders in four different countries. I was in charge of the UX-design, communicating with the external web agency that developed the site. I also was in charge of the general concept and built a hifi-prototype to be able to communicate my ideas with the development team in Finland and the stakeholders at Nordnet.\r\n\r\nI developed target group analysis, intervjued users in four different countries and kept in contact and got feeback during the entire project time from them. I built personas and scenarios to get my message through to the development team so they understood the challanges the diffrent uses had in the different countries.', 'Blog site', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '342-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-25 15:10:26', '2015-01-25 15:10:26', '', 342, 'http://www.mikaeleng.se/342-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(503, 1, '2014-12-15 14:07:28', '2014-12-15 14:07:28', 'Ett av mina längre projekt på Nordnet var Nordnets nya blogg. Den är utvecklad i WordPress och jag hade huvudansvar för kommunikationen med den externa webbyrån som utvecklade bloggen. Jag tillsammans med en Art Director tog fram själva konceptet och lösningsförslaget. Där jag stod för den interaktiva delarna och användabarhets-aspekten. För tydlig och snabb kommunikation med en webbyrå som befann sig i Finland byggde jag en <a href="http://share.axure.com/PKXFHS/Home.html" target="_blank">hi-fiprototyp i Axure</a> för att kunna diskutera och arbeta tillsammans över det långa avståndet. Samma prototyp användes också för att visa internt på Nordnet hur den nya blogportalen skulle se ut och fungera.\r\n\r\nOne of my major projects at Nordnet bank was developing their new blog site. The site was built in wordpress and had stakeholders in four different countries. I was in charge of the UX-design, communicating with the external web agency that developed the site. I also was in charge of the general concept and built a hifi-prototype to be able to communicate my ideas with the development team in Finland and the stakeholders at Nordnet.\r\n\r\nI developed target group analysis, intervjued users in four different countries and kept in contact and got feeback during the entire project time from them. I built personas and scenarios to get my message through to the development team so they understood the challanges the diffrent uses had in the different countries.', 'Nordnetbloggen', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '342-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-12-15 14:07:28', '2014-12-15 14:07:28', '', 342, 'http://www.mikaeleng.se/342-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
