(601, 1, '2015-01-28 12:14:02', '2015-01-28 12:14:02', 'på Nordnet Bank arbetade jag med utveckling av befintliga system och produkter, men även nya system och produkter för Nordnets Svenska, Finska, Norska och Danska webbplats. Jag tog fram målgruppsanalyser, utförde användartester, jobbade fram personas, scenarios, wireframes och uppföljning av mina utkast och prototyper.\r\n\r\nSom en del av UX-teamet på Nordnet sköter jag också kommunikationen mellan de externa och interna produktionsteam som bygger våra produkter. En del av mitt jobb innefattade också viss kampanjproducering I program som Flash, After Effects, PHP, javascript, CSS3 och HTML5.', 'Nordnet', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '593-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-28 12:14:02', '2015-01-28 12:14:02', '', 593, 'http://www.mikaeleng.se/593-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(602, 1, '2015-01-28 15:43:14', '2015-01-28 15:43:14', 'Medical Association knew that many of their members are surfing from phones and tablets. When the new site would be built on the target image was clear, it would work on e-reader, cell phone and laptop. Sublime therefore built the site in EPiServer CMS with responsive web design.\r\n\r\nThe project was also carried out a restructuring of the content and a new graphical form was developed. The new website is built according to a completely new structure has been clarified main navigation where, for example, the number of choices in the main menu is limited. During the restructuring were also prioritized target groups clear target market inputs and linked to pages with information that is relevant for them. One of the Medical Association\'s goal with this site is that it will generate new members. Member Function has lifted and is now clearly on the homepage.\r\n<h3>Challanges</h3>\r\nGeting the company to understand the use of target groups to focus the website and help the users find their needs so they will get a better experience.\r\n<h3>Experience</h3>\r\nMaking complex information structures visual for target groups and stakeholders. Geting them to understand the models and working close with the target groups.\r\n<h3>Conclusion</h3>\r\nBuilding an understanding for information architecture and target groups will help your communication with stakeholder. Get your stakeholders to participate in the workshops with target groups and card sorting meetings will make your job easier.', 'Doctors union website', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '375-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-01-28 15:43:14', '2015-01-28 15:43:14', '', 375, 'http://www.mikaeleng.se/375-revision-v1', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
